Burgess Jenkins https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Burgess_Jenkins 0 Burgess Jenkins (born October 24, 1973) is an American actor. He is known for work in the film Remember the Titans opposite Academy Award winner Denzel Washington; and as Hilary Swank's husband David Winter in The Reaping (2007).
